encies constitute separate editions; they seem more likely to be the same title available in different subscriptions.", "Also on microfilm: Athens, Ga. : University of Georgia Libraries.", "<March 9-April 1, 1921>, this title may have appeared also as part of Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : Daily), constituting the issue for certain days of the week.", "Merged with: Fitzgerald herald, to form: Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader.", "Vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921) (microfilm surrogate); title from masthead.", "Volume 69, number 37 (September 10, 1964) (microfilm surrogate).", "Fitzgerald herald (DLC)sn 89053304 (OCoLC)19965755", "Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader (DLC)sn 89053303 (OCoLC)19965743"], "other_formats": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp//gu/batch_gu_cookie_ver02/data/sn89053308/00517177258/1923092701/1923092701_1.xml", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn89053308/marcxml"], "other_title": ["Occasional issue may bear previous title: Leader enterprise and press"], "place_of_publication": "Fitzgerald, Georgia", "raw_lccn": "sn 89053308 ", "reel_numbers": ["00517177258"], "source_group": "ndnp/gu", "subjects": ["Fitzgerald (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Ben Hill County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Georgia--Ben Hill County", "Georgia--Fitzgerald", "United States--Georgia--Ben Hill--Fitzgerald"], "title": "The Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press (Fitzgerald, Georgia), September 27, 1923"}, "language": ["english"], "languages": [{"english": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=language:english&fo=json"}], "library_of_congress_control_number": "sn89053308", "location": ["ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "location_city": ["fitzgerald"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["ben hill"], "location_state": ["georgia"], "locations": [{"ben hill": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=location:ben+hill&fo=json"}, {"ben hill county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=location:ben+hill+county&fo=json"}, {"