es more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.504336, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn89053308, 1923-09-27, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/gu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["fitzgerald (ga.)", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Fitzgerald (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Ben Hill County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Georgia--Ben Hill County", "Georgia--Fitzgerald", "United States--Georgia--Ben Hill--Fitzgerald"], "subjects": [{"ben hill": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ben+hill&fo=json"}, {"ben hill county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ben+hill+county&fo=json"}, {"ben hill county (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ben+hill+county+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"fitzgerald": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:fitzgerald&fo=json"}, {"fitzgerald (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:fitzgerald+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"georgia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:georgia&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T17:41:16.524Z", "title": "The Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press (Fitzgerald, Georgia), September 27, 1923", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053308/1923-09-27/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053308/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn89053308", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/6d9bf45c-9ba4-51b4-a38e-b838603e3b81"], "batch": ["gu_cookie_ver02"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1921", "description": ["Weekly, January 12, 1922-September 10, 1964 Began with: Vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921); ceased with: Volume 69, number 37 (September 10, 1964). \"Official organ of the city of Fitzgerald.\"--vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921), page [4]. For some issues in April 1921, stated frequency is \"published daily, tri-weekly.\" Cannot be detemined whether the two frequencies constitute separate editions; they seem more likely to be the same title available in different subscriptions. Also on microfilm: Athens, Ga. : University of Georgia Libraries. <March 9-April 1, 1921>, this title may have appeared also as part of Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : Daily), constituting the issue for certain days of the week. Merged with: Fitzgerald herald, to form: Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader. Vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921) (microfilm surrogate); title from masthead. Volume 69, number 37 (September 10, 1964) (microfilm surrogate). Fitzgerald herald (DLC)sn 89053304 (OCoLC)19965755 Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader (DLC)sn 89053303 (OCoLC)19965743"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.512Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-05", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-05"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053308/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [31.7148055, -83.2515932], "location": ["ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-83.2515932, 31.7148055], "number": ["1", "404", "online resource", "19965806", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2024-05-12t17:32:27.269094", "sn89053309", "sn89053304", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053308/1927-05-26/ed-1/", "microfilm service copy", "sn89053303", "2025-07-01t13:41:15.400000", "sn89053306", "sn89053308", "univ of georgia", "microfilm master", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053308/1921-03-09/ed-1/", "2995-9888"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Occasional issue may bear previous title: Leader enterprise and press"], "partof": ["catalog", "chronicling america", "the fitzgerald leader enterprise and press (fitzgerald, georgia) 1921-1964", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 83.1981, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn89053308", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["fitzgerald (ga.)", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-22T07:55:19.186Z", "title": "The Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053308/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271009/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1895", "dates": ["[1895 TO 1912]"], "description": ["Triweekly, June 13, 1903-Apr. 13, 1912 Print began in December 1895; ceased with volume XVII, number 51 (April 13, 1912). Publisher: Nettie C. Hall, <1897>. Merged with: Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : 1910), to form: Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.). Volume VII, Number [?] (October 3, 1902); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Volume XVII, Number 51 (April 13, 1912) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : 1910) 2995-9705 (DLC) 2024271010 (OCoLC)1288157538 Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.) 2995-9721 (DLC) 2024271011 (OCoLC)1350137676"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271009/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["irwin", "ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "online resource", "1348950650", "2024271010", "2024271011", "2024271009", "2995-9683"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["fitzgerald enterprise (fitzgerald, georgia) 1895-1912 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 73.91898, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["irwin", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "journaux", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "Fitzgerald enterprise", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271009/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271010/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "18??", "dates": ["[1800 TO 1912]"], "description": ["Semiweekly, <Jan. 4, 1911>-Apr. 12, 1912 Ceased with vol. XVII, no. 27 (April 12, 1912). Published also as a daily. Publisher: B.F. Knapp and J.G. Knapp, <January 28, 1910>. Merged with: Fitzgerald enterprise, to form: Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.). Vol. XVII, No. 24 (April 2, 1912); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XVII, No. 27 (April 12, 1912) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald enterprise 2995-9683 (DLC) 2024271009 (OCoLC)1348950650 Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.) 2995-9721 (DLC) 2024271011 (OCoLC)1350137676"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:01.956Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271010/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["irwin", "ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "number": ["2995-9705", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2024271010", "2024271011", "1288157538", "2024271009"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Issues published Feb. 1-Mar. 11, 1911 with title: Semiweekly Fitzgerald leader"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the fitzgerald leader (fitzgerald, ben hill county georgia) 18??-1912 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["semiweekly"], "score": 73.91898, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["irwin", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "journaux", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "periodical", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Fitzgerald leader", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271010/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271012/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1915", "dates": ["[1915 TO 1915]"], "description": ["Triweekly Began with vol. XX, no. 134 (Nov. 10, 1915); ceased with vol. XX, no. 140 (Nov. 22, 1915). Formed by the union of: Leader-Enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.), and: Fitzgerald press. Vol. XX, No. 134 (Nov. 10, 1915); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XX, No. 140 (Nov. 10, 1915) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Leader enterprise and press 2995-9799 (DLC) 2024271013 (OCoLC)1350104569"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271012/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "number": ["1350137653", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2024271011", "2024271013", "2995-9748", "2024271012"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the leader-enterprise and fitzgerald press (fitzgerald, ben hill county, georgia) 1915-1915 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 73.91898, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["fitzgerald (ga.)", "journaux", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Leader-enterprise and Fitzgerald press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271012/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1915", "dates": ["[1915 TO 1921]"], "description": ["Triweekly Began with vol. XX, no. 141 (Nov. 24, 1915); ceased in March 1921. Vol. XX, No. 141 (Nov. 24, 1915); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XXVI, No. 29 (March 11, 1921) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press 2995-9896 (DLC) 2024271014 (OCoLC)1350136980"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "number": ["1350104569", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "online resource", "2024271015", "2024271014", "2024271013", "2995-9799", "2024271012"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the leader enterprise and press (fitzgerald, ben hill county, georgia) 1915-1921 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 73.91898, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["fitzgerald (ga.)", "journaux", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The leader enterprise and press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1921", "dates": ["[1921 TO 1964]"], "description": ["Weekly, January 12, 1922-September 10, 1964 Began with vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921); ceased with v. 69, no. 37 (Sept. 10, 1964). \"Official organ of the city of Fitzgerald.\"--vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921), page [4]. Publisher: Fitzgerald Leader Company, Inc., April 4, 1963-September 10, 1964. For some issues in April 1921, stated frequency is \"published daily, tri-weekly.\" Cannot be detemined whether the two frequencies constitute separate editions; they seem more likely to be the same title available in different subscriptions. <March 9-April 1, 1921>, this title may have appeared also as part of Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : Daily), constituting the issue for certain days of the week. Merged with: Fitzgerald herald, to form: Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader. Vol. XXVI, No. 29 (March 9, 1921); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XXXVIII, No. 21 (May 26, 1927) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald herald Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/", "image_url": [], "index": 9, "language": ["english"], "location": ["ben hill county", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "number": ["2995-9896", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "online resource", "1350136980", "2024271015", "2024271014", "2024271013"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Occasional issue may bear previous title: Leader enterprise and press"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the fitzgerald leader enterprise and press (fitzgerald, georgia) 1921-1964 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 73.91898, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["fitzgerald (ga.)", "journaux", "ben hill county", "newspapers", "ben hill county (ga.)", "georgia", "ben hill", "fitzgerald", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/"}], "next_resource": {"label": "Next Issue", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89053308/1923-10-04/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1"}, "options": {"access_group": [""], "access_group_raw": "", "all": null, "api_version": "1", "app_context": null, "application_version": "$Revision$", "attribute": null, "attribute!": null, "attribute_map": null, "cache_tags": ["ndnp/gu", "digital-library-of-georgia-awardee", "newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-05", "catalog", "united-s